Description: `sasr` is a package to provide SAS interface in R, through `SASpy`(https://sassoftware.github.io/saspy/) and `reticulate`(https://rstudio.github.io/reticulate/).
  This package help you create SAS sessions, execute SAS code in remote SAS servers, retrieve execution results and log, and exchange datasets between SAS and R.
  It also helps you install `SASpy` and create configuration file for the connection.
